议的制定者为以色列的未来描绘了严峻的愿景。事实证明它非常准确</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</link><description>《奥斯陆协议》的缔造者之一罗恩·庞达克 (Ron Pundak) 在 1999 年对以色列 2025 年的情况做出了噩梦般的预测。今天，在他去世十年后，这一切已经非常接近现实了</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 23:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</guid></item><item><title>甚至在哈马斯做出回应之前，内塔尼亚胡就试图破坏人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</link><description>以色列总理渴望在任何协议中发挥作用，他的同谋贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇也有同样的态度。 -法西斯立法</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 21:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在加沙人质协议第一阶段放弃了持久停火的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</link><description>真主党周五还表示，一旦加沙地带休战生效，真主党将停止战斗。然而，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，双方之间“仍然存在分歧”</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 20:58:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</guid></item><item><title>如何在不影响间谍的情况下处理情报警告：阿什拉夫·马尔万的教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-address-an-intelligence-warning-without-putting-the-spy-at-risk/000